# Pet Adoption Platform (GUI)

## Project Overview
The Pet Adoption Platform is a JavaFX-based desktop application that helps users adopt pets. It allows users to view available pets, register as adopters, and search for pets by breed or name.

## Features
- **User Registration**: Users can register with their personal details.
- **Pet Adoption**: Users can browse available pets and initiate the adoption process.
- **Pet Search**: Allows users to search for pets by type, name, etc.
- **Data Validation**: Ensures that all input fields are valid before submission.

## Installation Instructions
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/pet-adoption-platform.git
java -jar PetAdoptionApp.jar

